# Kubernetes Tips
# Format: alias|old_command_pattern|description|example

k|kubectl |Short alias for kubectl|k get pods
kgp|kubectl get pods|List pods|kgp
kgs|kubectl get services|List services|kgs
kgd|kubectl get deployments|List deployments|kgd
kdp|kubectl describe pod|Describe a pod|kdp my-pod
kds|kubectl describe service|Describe a service|kds my-service
kdd|kubectl describe deployment|Describe a deployment|kdd my-deployment
kl|kubectl logs|View pod logs|kl my-pod -f
kex|kubectl exec|Execute command in pod|kex -it my-pod -- /bin/sh
